    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "JALENTE\nJAL INTERNATIONAL FLIGHT SCHEDULE\nJAL E$RE / JALWAYS JALDI17\nJAL\n2008\n9.1 - 10.25\nJolL\nInternational reservation\n0120-25-5931\nDomestic reservation\nSIN CHA 22A\n0120-25-5971\nJALA-L^-9.115411\nwww.jal.co.jp\noneworld\nmember",
      "JOL\nJAL EATE\nJALWAYS JALTI17\n9/1-10/25HR\n0815t\nInternational Passenger Timetable:\nAdditional Information [Sep.1~ Oct.25 Edition]\nP71•72 #P#-E702*7\n#ALUJALTUA\n==-3-78#~ =#≥752/73*97~\n$#==1-3-7$ JL006/JL0051€\n871~10900 3#0#1.8710500A\nJL002/JL0011#\n99130#1\nP71 • 72 In-flight Services\nJAL To Introduce State-of-the Art\nFirst Class Suite \u0026 Business Class Seat\nIntroduction of 777-300ER on US Routes Fitted with Best Seating and Service in the skies.\nBrand new 777-300ER aircraft will start operating Tokyo-New York route\nfrom August, Tokyo-San Francisco route from September.\nThe route information for new 777-300ER aircraft.\n• New York=Tokyo JL005/JL006\nstarting Aug.1, 2008\nService is available every other day until Aug. 10,\nand will be available daily from Aug. 11.\n• San Francisco=Tokyo JL001/JL002\nstarting Sep. 13, 2008\nAvailable daily.\n(Notice) Operating aircraft and seating configurations are subject\nto change without prior notice."
    ],
